Great game; hidden system, DLC was free in this sale, thank you for the free map exposer;

My rating: 83 / 100.
(+) It is one of the best NFS games in last decade;
(+) Good graphics, decent soundtracks, very arcadish game;
(+) Las-Vegas-like area is well thought out and is fun to play;
(+) Nice variety of race types and car classes too choose;
(+) Enjoyable online modes to play with friends;
(–) Steering could be more improved, too wobbly cars;
(–) Annoying childish dialogues between main characters;
